{
  "stem": "1354.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were getting up 5:00 in the morning to go, maybe they would give us some kind of a-- a job to get some papers, because only people who were working could get-- be legally in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyhow, so that's-- that time when they gave me the job, by in [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was for Schindler.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in '42.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was summer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was summer, maybe even spring.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "May, June, something like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So me and-- and my sister, the one who had the baby, they sent her to Kabel to another factory.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My youngest sister, Dora, I was waking her up in the morning and telling her to come on get up-- she was only two, three years younger than me-- come on, let's get up.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She says, I'm not getting up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not working for Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How old were you at this time?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the war broke out I was 14.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in '39.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was 16? 17?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well anyhow, so still from ghetto, I was going back and forth with a group, you know, we-- with a German, back and forth, working shifts day night-- one week days, one week nights. 12 hours, 12 hours a-- a shift.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in '42, in-- in-- in-- that was in-- in fall, I think, my brother came to the house, my father came, and they-- my brother said, I heard something is-- he had a hint from a German that at night the ghetto will be surrounded, and they're going to take out-- liquidate, some-- some people.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was at the time on the night shift.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father and my brother gave me-- they told me, you-- you better go to work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You don't stay.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
